{"id": "art-46", "label": "Art. 46", "title": "Art. 46: Regimul anulabilităţii", "slug": "art-46", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_938117817\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1287\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_938117817\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 46: Regimul\nanulabilit&#259;&#355;ii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1999711716\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1286\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1999711716\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Ac&#355;iunea în anulare poate fi exercitat&#259; de\nreprezentantul legal, de minorul care a împlinit vârsta de 14 ani, de cel care\nbeneficiaz&#259; de consiliere judiciar&#259;, precum &#351;i de ocrotitorul\nlegal sau de consiliul de familie, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_974630778\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1285\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_974630778\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Atunci când actul s-a încheiat f&#259;r&#259;\nautorizarea instan&#355;ei de tutel&#259;, necesar&#259; potrivit legii,\naceasta va sesiza procurorul în vederea exercit&#259;rii ac&#355;iunii în\nanulare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_193405014\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1284\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_193405014\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Persoana capabil&#259; de a contracta nu poate opune\nanulabilitatea contractului &#351;i nici exercita ac&#355;iunea în anulare,\nîns&#259; poate cere men&#355;inerea contractului &#351;i reducerea sau\nmajorarea propriei presta&#355;ii, dup&#259; caz.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}